    "description": "INTEGRATED TEST CASES for Converge.fi Stablecoin Simulations ($100K Reserve)\n\nThese tests validate end-to-end behavior of the ACTUS simulation pipeline,\nbehavioral models, market risk models, and the mint→halt→restore lifecycle.\n\nTEST CATEGORIES:\n  TC-01: Reference Index CRUD operations\n  TC-02: Behavioral Model registration + verification\n  TC-03: Scenario assembly + verification\n  TC-04: Simulation execution + event validation\n  TC-05: Health check pass (mint succeeds)\n  TC-06: Health check fail (mint blocked)\n  TC-07: Health restore (mint resumed)\n  TC-08: Multi-contract maturity ladder events\n  TC-09: Market risk (rate shock) impact\n  TC-10: Behavioral model callback verification\n\nPrerequisites:\n  - ACTUS Risk Service running on localhost:8082\n  - ACTUS Sim Engine running on localhost:8083\n  - MongoDB running on localhost:27018\n  - OR: Replace localhost with 34.203.247.32 for AWS\n\nOpen Postman Console (Ctrl+Alt+C) before running.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
